{"id":169129,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/global-voices-古巴：捍卫“白色妇女运动”/","date":"2011-07-28T01:30:24Z","modified":"2011-07-28T01:30:24Z","title":"Global Voices | 古巴：捍卫“白色妇女运动”","content":"<p><p>古巴的博客们持续不断地更新<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/18/cuba-female-activists-reportedly-beatendetained/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/18/cuba-female-activists-reportedly-beatendetained/\">近期受打压的</a>白色妇女运动（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ladies_in_White\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ladies_in_White\">Las Damas de Blanco</a>）相关文章，并指出部份参加运动的成员“<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://babalublog.com/2011/07/ladies-in-white-violently-attacked-yesterday-by-castro-state-security/\" href=\"http://babalublog.com/2011/07/ladies-in-white-violently-attacked-yesterday-by-castro-state-security/\">在离开教堂时被卡斯特罗国家安全局（Castro State Security）的人员攻击与毒打</a>”。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://coalitionofcubanamericanwomen.blogspot.com/2011/07/ladies-in-white-beaten-dragged-and.html\" href=\"http://coalitionofcubanamericanwomen.blogspot.com/2011/07/ladies-in-white-beaten-dragged-and.html\">美国古巴裔妇女联盟</a>发布新闻稿指责该次攻击事件，新闻稿包含了一段该事件当事人Tania Montoya Vázquez讲述该次经验的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.martinoticias.com/noticias/Agreden-a-opositoras-en-Santiago-de-Cuba--125710308.html\" href=\"http://www.martinoticias.com/noticias/Agreden-a-opositoras-en-Santiago-de-Cuba--125710308.html\">录音片段</a>[西语]。El Cafe Cubano博客<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://elcubanocafe.blogspot.com/2011/07/cuba-ladies-in-white-beaten-dragged.html\" href=\"http://elcubanocafe.blogspot.com/2011/07/cuba-ladies-in-white-beaten-dragged.html\">重新发布了该联盟的新闻稿</a>。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/globovision/4443738026/\"><img title=\"The Ladies in White shout slogans.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/ladies-in-white-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"The Ladies in White shout slogans. Image by Flickr user Globovisión (CC BY-NC 2.0).\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></a></p>\n<p>The Ladies in White shout slogans. Image by Flickr user Globovisión (CC BY-NC 2.0).</p>\n</div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://babalublog.com/2011/07/attack-on-the-ladies-in-white-a-desperate-plea-for-help-recorded-during-the-attack/\" href=\"http://babalublog.com/2011/07/attack-on-the-ladies-in-white-a-desperate-plea-for-help-recorded-during-the-attack/\">芭芭鲁（Babalu）</a>针对昨天攻击事件发生时，白色妇女运动的领袖Tania Montoya Vazquez打电话到Hablalo Sin Miedo博客的录音档评论：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>你可以听到她声音里的绝望和恐惧。即使你不会说或听不懂西班牙语，她的声音语调和背景的尖叫便是一笔卡斯特罗独裁统治的纪录。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>这一事件引起了其他社群的强烈抗议，国际自由青年联合会的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://iflry.org/blogs/mos/archive/2011/07/18/Condemnation-of-Cuba_2700_s-Continuing-Crackdown.aspx\" href=\"http://iflry.org/blogs/mos/archive/2011/07/18/Condemnation-of-Cuba_2700_s-Continuing-Crackdown.aspx\">声明如下</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Belkis Cantillo Ramirez手臂中枪，而其他人则被警棍、石块等物毒打。在这场暴力行动中，Tania Montoya和Rodaisa Corrioso被当局逮捕。除了这两个勇敢的女性，十三名该组织的成员，包括Belkis Cantillo Ramirez，正在当地医院接受治疗。 国际自由青年联合会（IFLRY）以最强烈的措辞谴责这些袭击事件。白色妇女运动是一个和平运动。以这种残暴镇压回应这种非暴力运动，充分显现了卡斯特罗 政权的专制。如果这些攻击并没有获得当局授权，那么必须立即着手调查并给予深远的审判。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>声明接着要求“必须立即无条件释放Tania Montoya和Rodaisa Corrioso”，芭芭鲁（Babalu）“用更多的照片”（包括照片）写了<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://babalublog.com/2011/07/ladies-in-white-beaten-dragged-and-stoned/\" href=\"http://babalublog.com/2011/07/ladies-in-white-beaten-dragged-and-stoned/\">另一篇文章说</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>今天上午快速审视一些“古巴专家”的网站，没有一篇提及此次暴力攻击手无寸铁的勇敢女性的事件。这些“专家”的狭隘反映了卡斯特罗政权的狭隘…他们不愿意提及暴行的真相…</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://marcmasferrer.typepad.com/uncommon_sense/2011/07/castro-thugs-attack-ladies-in-white-outside-of-church.html\" href=\"http://marcmasferrer.typepad.com/uncommon_sense/2011/07/castro-thugs-attack-ladies-in-white-outside-of-church.html\">Uncommon Sense</a>语重心长地提出：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>一位值得称道的古巴圣地亚哥天主教会发言人<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.ddcuba.com/derechos-humanos/5877-fuente-de-la-iglesia-confirma-la-paliza-de-el-cobre-contra-dieciseis-damas-de-\" href=\"http://www.ddcuba.com/derechos-humanos/5877-fuente-de-la-iglesia-confirma-la-paliza-de-el-cobre-contra-dieciseis-damas-de-\">证实了该报导</a>，并谴责攻击事件。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>这是一个有趣的观察：芭芭鲁（Babalu）对于<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.usatoday.com/news/opinion/forum/2011-07-18-castro-cuba-cardinal-ortega_n.htm\" href=\"http://www.usatoday.com/news/opinion/forum/2011-07-18-castro-cuba-cardinal-ortega_n.htm\">美国今日报</a>报 导的反应，该报导建议“后古巴卡斯特罗政权将需要一个被社会信任的力量，帮助这个国家进入一个新的时代，没有流血或动乱。红衣主教Jaime Lucas Ortega y Alamino，古巴首都的大主教，就是那个人。身为糖厂工人的儿子，Ortega是唯一有能力填补权力真空的人。”</p>\n<p>芭芭鲁（Babalu）<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://babalublog.com/2011/07/usa-todays-purgative-elixir-cardinal-jaime-ortega-for-president-of-cuba/\" href=\"http://babalublog.com/2011/07/usa-todays-purgative-elixir-cardinal-jaime-ortega-for-president-of-cuba/\">强烈反对</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>总统平斯基（Pinsky）强烈展示纯粹的无知和傲慢的蔑视，当代被视为古巴史上最腐败及最容易妥协的人，忽视了历史悠久的古巴领导人，如Dr. Oscar Elias Biscet，不像Ortega，并没有损害他的原则，或让自己被用作独裁统治的政治工具。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://elcubanocafe.blogspot.com/2011/07/looking-other-way.html\" href=\"http://elcubanocafe.blogspot.com/2011/07/looking-other-way.html\">El Cafe Cubano</a>博客同意此观点：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>上周日在“古巴圣地亚哥，古巴东部省份的城市，亲民主活动的妇女在El Cobre教堂参加大规模的弥撒后，于古巴的街头被国家安全人员野蛮地殴打和辱骂攻击，她们在那里为古巴的政治犯和古巴的自由祈祷。“ 天主教会​​沉默，寻找其他的方式…</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>毫无疑问，古巴侨民将继续关注事件发展，并提供白色妇女运动网络支持。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Portnoy\">Portnoy</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/janine-mendes-franco/\" title=\"文章导读 Janine Mendes-Franco\">Janine Mendes-Franco</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ravi/\" title=\"文章导读 Ravi\">Ravi</a> </span> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/07/19/cuba-defending-las-damas/\" title=\"阅读原文 [en]\">阅读原文 [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/07/28/9567/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%8F%A4%E5%B7%B4%EF%BC%9A%E6%8D%8D%E5%8D%AB%E2%80%9C%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E2%80%9D&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F07%2F28%2F9567%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F07%2F28%2F9567%2F&#038;desc=%E5%8F%A4%E5%B7%B4%EF%BC%9A%E6%8D%8D%E5%8D%AB%E2%80%9C%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E2%80%9D\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F07%2F28%2F9567%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F07%2F28%2F9567%2F&#038;text=%E5%8F%A4%E5%B7%B4%EF%BC%9A%E6%8D%8D%E5%8D%AB%E2%80%9C%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E2%80%9D&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F07%2F28%2F9567%2F&#038;title=%E5%8F%A4%E5%B7%B4%EF%BC%9A%E6%8D%8D%E5%8D%AB%E2%80%9C%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8%E2%80%9D\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.g